Swapmeet (1982)

Starring: Jack Brier, Cilla Pink, Lynn True, Susie Walker.
Categories: Classic
Date Added: 1982
(858 Mb)

The mansion that a young couple inherits has been, they find, a center for sophisticated depravity. They get immersed in voyeurism and hedonistic love triangles with their willing servants. Eventually the entire household, including the guests at a formal dinner party, get caught up in the antics. SWAPMEET puts you right in the action at a free-for-all orgy of smoldering sensuality and raunchy sex. An offer you can't refuse!
